        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "Apart from the default colorscheme, the bundled themes are not maintained by us but taken (with only strictly necessary minor adjustments) from the Vim runtime, which in turn imports them from https://github.com/vim/colorschemes.\n\nWe are definitely not going to start bundling other external colorschemes; that is a barrel without bottom.\n",
